Pain Point
Topic: Applications.
Company: TELUS Corporation, Vancouver, BC
Opportunity: A front line source has indicated that the organization is experiencing pain related to the quality/reliability of its application development process. The organization is likely to spend to address this issue. (Live on 05/15/2017)
Update: We are exploring methodologies to address this issue.




2017-06-20
Project Scoop
Topic: Data Warehousing.
Company: TELUS Corporation, Vancouver, BC
Opportunity: A front-line source has indicated that data warehouse solutions are a spending priority. The organization has selected Fujitsu Enterprise Solutions and is currently implementing. This initiative will take place company-wide. The organization uses contingent/contract workers for technology initiatives. (Live on 02/01/2017)
Update: We are now selecting vendors.




