Pain Point
Topic: Applications.
Company: TELUS Corporation, Vancouver, BC
Opportunity: A front line source has indicated that the organization is experiencing pain related to the complexity of enterprise application portfolios. (Live on 04/20/2017)
Update: We are creating a new team to address this issue.







